    "title": "Add \"maxuploadtargettimeframe\" to change the timeframe considered by \"maxuploadtarget\"",
    "body": "### Please describe the feature you'd like to see added.\r\n\r\nThe \"maxuploadtarget\"\r\n#Tries to keep outbound traffic under the given target per 24h (one day). \r\n\r\nBut many ISPs that does not have unlimited traffic, account it by month. So it will be a handy setting to avoid the calculating of the amount transferred in the billing period. This new setting can be specified in days.",
